# Ionic Capacitor Angular Skills

Use `skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md` as the canonical skill instruction file.

Follow `AGENTS.md` first, then the smallest matching skill. Use `feature-delivery-orchestrator` as the baseline when a task crosses multiple topics.

Do not duplicate skill bodies into Cursor rules. `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>` should remain an alias to `skills/<skill-name>`.
